"If there are cases you are talking about, it could be a breach of the terms of the contract which we would deal with and might result in the termination of cooperation with the company concerned," Martin Kemr answered our question about this problem.
However, it is unlikely that a similar activity towards responsible people from mobile operators could have been achieved.
